# The native Cubism extension is a required runtime dependency. The generic
# bin/ rule above must not hide its distributable Windows binary.
!addons/gd_cubism/bin/
!addons/gd_cubism/bin/.gitignore
!addons/gd_cubism/bin/libgd_cubism.windows.release.x86_64.dll
